{"tid":1428884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五支旗干收起晒所有旗","createTime":"2019-08-07T11:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T11:38:09.000Z","uid":248003,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"57377db60ba710af0092a01c58b6ae514c8f648e","tid":1428884,"uid":248003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:21:36.000Z","msg":"有五個吉位，升咩旗好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【尖沙咀實況】五支旗桿<br />\n<br />\n浸會大學學生會會長方仲賢因購買鐳射筆被捕，事件亦繼續發酵，有天文學界組織趁今日為七夕，號召群眾帶備鐳射觀星筆到尖沙咀太空館觀星。  <br />\n<br />\n曾經兩次被示威者拆除五星旗的五支旗桿，今日已經早有準備，索性所有旗都收起，令「拆旗手」及「護旗手」都無事可做。<br />\n<br />\n（7:00 PM）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YGfDLAB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYGfDLAB.png&h=e6a98997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2514031518660000?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F420361564693683%2Fposts%2F2514031518660000%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=60e06bbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2514031518660000?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"72f748aa6f24b2c70c28cbed594b850684f21860","tid":1428884,"uid":248003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa87f972768b723df5aeafc2d0a14c812097d190","tid":1428884,"uid":248003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd4a295489a2121fd3a9a07ba269d79676ce864","tid":1428884,"uid":70217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:27:36.000Z","msg":"光、復、香、港、logo flag"},{"pid":"598c24caebe13a7707ff6cde97aefcdcba9fd4ca","tid":1428884,"uid":29132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:34:56.0